42
00:03:50,000 --> 00:03:50,960
Hand in hand,

43
00:03:51,400 --> 00:03:52,600
I shall grow old
with snow-white hair with you.

44
00:04:07,400 --> 00:04:08,720
I didn't expect you

45
00:04:09,000 --> 00:04:10,240
to prepare all this.

46
00:04:22,440 --> 00:04:23,480
You suffered in your youth

47
00:04:23,480 --> 00:04:24,520
with no family left.

48
00:04:24,880 --> 00:04:26,080
Now that we're married,

49
00:04:26,080 --> 00:04:27,360
it's only right to inform the ancestors

50
00:04:28,280 --> 00:04:29,320
and put their minds at ease.

51
00:04:31,760 --> 00:04:33,240
I still remember that day,

52
00:04:33,440 --> 00:04:34,800
when you stood in the rain

53
00:04:35,160 --> 00:04:36,000
holding an umbrella.

54
00:04:37,240 --> 00:04:38,480
The sky was clear and wide,

55
00:04:40,160 --> 00:04:41,200
but it seemed like

56
00:04:42,560 --> 00:04:44,000
you were the only person in the world.

57
00:04:45,640 --> 00:04:47,080
I thought at that moment,

58
00:04:47,320 --> 00:04:48,400
what if

59
00:04:50,360 --> 00:04:52,640
that tragedy never happened

60
00:04:52,640 --> 00:04:53,440
when you were young?

61
00:04:55,560 --> 00:04:58,760
You'd have grown up

62
00:04:59,720 --> 00:05:02,040
in a loving and prominent family

63
00:05:07,360 --> 00:05:09,920
and become
the most dazzling man in Andu.

64
00:05:16,080 --> 00:05:18,520
Maybe you'd have

65
00:05:18,520 --> 00:05:19,440
married me

66
00:05:19,680 --> 00:05:20,720
through a proper match

67
00:05:20,880 --> 00:05:21,840
arranged by our parents.

68
00:05:28,880 --> 00:05:31,040
Maybe you and my brother
would've become friends,

69
00:05:31,240 --> 00:05:32,280
practicing swordplay

70
00:05:32,440 --> 00:05:33,520
and laughing together.

71
00:06:13,840 --> 00:06:15,040
What if?

72
00:06:16,480 --> 00:06:17,400
These will never happen.

73
00:06:32,880 --> 00:06:34,040
Did you know

74
00:06:37,800 --> 00:06:40,320
my mother was the second daughter
of the Duke?

75
00:06:42,080 --> 00:06:42,880
The Empress

76
00:06:44,240 --> 00:06:45,640
was her elder sister.

77
00:06:48,720 --> 00:06:52,280
Even if we could go back in time
a thousand times,

78
00:06:53,360 --> 00:06:54,320
the Na family

79
00:06:56,680 --> 00:06:58,200
would never have survived.

80
00:07:00,200 --> 00:07:01,480
Do you know why?

81
00:07:04,520 --> 00:07:07,000
Because I wasn't Na Cheng'an's son.

82
00:07:10,520 --> 00:07:12,080
I'm the Emperor's illegitimate child.

83
00:07:14,840 --> 00:07:16,920
Back then, the Empress had no children.

84
00:07:18,000 --> 00:07:19,760
So she drugged my mother
and sent her into the palace,

85
00:07:20,600 --> 00:07:23,040
intending for her

86
00:07:23,160 --> 00:07:24,760
to bear a son

87
00:07:25,040 --> 00:07:26,640
who could be the Crown Prince.

88
00:07:29,640 --> 00:07:31,240
But who could've predicted

89
00:07:33,600 --> 00:07:35,200
she'd become pregnant
at the same time?

90
00:07:43,800 --> 00:07:45,520
It's born.

91
00:07:45,560 --> 00:07:46,400
It's born, Madam.

92
00:07:58,240 --> 00:07:58,840
Madam,

93
00:07:59,560 --> 00:08:00,600
it's a boy.

94
00:08:01,240 --> 00:08:02,200
The baby's face is

95
00:08:03,240 --> 00:08:04,520
covered with black hair.

96
00:08:18,520 --> 00:08:19,440
A monster.

97
00:08:23,920 --> 00:08:24,720
Don't be afraid.

98
00:08:25,480 --> 00:08:27,080
Mother will protect you.

99
00:08:28,880 --> 00:08:31,560
In the 14th year of Tianyan,

100
00:08:31,560 --> 00:08:34,200
I, the monster, was born.

101
00:08:38,040 --> 00:08:38,920
A year later,

102
00:08:40,560 --> 00:08:41,080
the Empress gave birth

103
00:08:41,080 --> 00:08:42,440
to Li Chi.

104
00:08:43,440 --> 00:08:45,640
Contaminated by poison,

105
00:08:47,960 --> 00:08:50,120
I had no value left.

106
00:08:51,840 --> 00:08:55,880
My mother thought if she kept
my true identity a secret,

107
00:08:55,980 --> 00:08:56,560
That way!

108
00:08:56,560 --> 00:08:57,880
the Empress might tolerate me.

109
00:08:59,120 --> 00:08:59,600
But,

110
00:09:02,480 --> 00:09:05,200
my identity remained a future trouble.

111
00:09:06,160 --> 00:09:06,800
Because of me,

112
00:09:07,280 --> 00:09:11,000
the Empress and the Duke
slaughtered the entire Na family.

113
00:09:24,480 --> 00:09:27,560
I used to resent the heavens
for poisoning you

114
00:09:27,560 --> 00:09:28,640
and making you lack emotion or desire.

115
00:09:29,000 --> 00:09:31,800
Now I see it may have been a blessing.

116
00:09:34,600 --> 00:09:35,720
You have to live.

117
00:09:37,200 --> 00:09:39,840
Jinci, let's play a game.

118
00:09:41,440 --> 00:09:43,600
No matter what you see,

119
00:09:44,120 --> 00:09:45,200
don't speak

120
00:09:45,440 --> 00:09:47,080
or move, do you hear me?

121
00:09:48,080 --> 00:09:50,160
No matter how unfair fate is to you,

122
00:09:51,200 --> 00:09:53,800
never forget the kindness in your heart.

123
00:09:57,280 --> 00:09:58,080
Quickly!

124
00:10:10,040 --> 00:10:11,520
After my mother committed suicide,

125
00:10:11,840 --> 00:10:14,760
a loyal servant of the Na family
swapped me

126
00:10:15,200 --> 00:10:16,320
with his own child.

127
00:10:17,360 --> 00:10:18,840
Sometimes, I wonder

128
00:10:21,280 --> 00:10:23,720
why I wasn't Na Cheng'an

129
00:10:23,720 --> 00:10:25,200
and Lin Lan's child,

130
00:10:26,560 --> 00:10:28,600
even if they were just ordinary people.

131
00:10:43,200 --> 00:10:44,360
The blood of the royal family...

132
00:10:46,320 --> 00:10:47,560
The blood of the royal family

133
00:10:51,840 --> 00:10:53,040
is so unbearable.

134
00:10:55,200 --> 00:10:57,480
The blood that flows in my veins

135
00:10:57,680 --> 00:10:59,480
disgusts me

136
00:11:00,040 --> 00:11:01,400
every moment

137
00:11:02,880 --> 00:11:04,360
of every day.

138
00:11:10,280 --> 00:11:11,040
Maybe

139
00:11:13,400 --> 00:11:15,560
I was never meant to be born.

140
00:11:25,440 --> 00:11:26,440
Yin,

141
00:11:30,400 --> 00:11:31,400
did you know?

142
00:11:34,480 --> 00:11:35,760
If I

143
00:11:37,480 --> 00:11:38,680
had died young,

144
00:11:41,360 --> 00:11:42,880
the Na family might have survived.

145
00:11:46,720 --> 00:11:47,680
Na Jinci,

146
00:11:47,680 --> 00:11:48,840
listen to me.

147
00:11:50,480 --> 00:11:52,560
Your family has been
noble for generations.

148
00:11:52,960 --> 00:11:55,320
Your mother gave her life
to protect you.

149
00:11:55,680 --> 00:11:58,560
You're as worthy as any nobleman,

150
00:11:58,560 --> 00:11:59,480
you know?

151
00:12:01,680 --> 00:12:03,280
Being poisoned isn't your fault

152
00:12:03,400 --> 00:12:04,960
and you can't choose your bloodline.

153
00:12:05,720 --> 00:12:06,520
But

154
00:12:08,560 --> 00:12:10,680
you can't punish yourself with hatred.

155
00:12:38,640 --> 00:12:41,600
This was bestowed by His Majesty.

156
00:12:43,080 --> 00:12:45,040
How dare you?

157
00:12:45,760 --> 00:12:48,040
I wouldn't dare. Your Majesty,
please see the truth.

158
00:12:49,160 --> 00:12:49,960
What?

159
00:12:51,160 --> 00:12:53,040
Are you saying I've slandered you?

160
00:12:53,640 --> 00:12:54,440
I wouldn't dare.

161
00:12:54,840 --> 00:12:56,680
But many in the palace can testify

162
00:12:56,920 --> 00:13:00,040
I never went near the tea cup
bestowed by His Majesty.

163
00:13:02,920 --> 00:13:04,320
Many can testify?

164
00:13:05,640 --> 00:13:07,400
Did any of you see it

165
00:13:08,000 --> 00:13:09,640
or is willing to testify?

166
00:13:27,320 --> 00:13:28,440
Step forward.

167
00:13:56,560 --> 00:13:59,200
Lift your head
and show me your face.

168
00:14:13,760 --> 00:14:15,400
Someone, give her thirty slaps.

169
00:14:25,760 --> 00:14:28,760
I want to see
if that little face of yours,

170
00:14:28,760 --> 00:14:30,160
can still seduce His Majesty

171
00:14:30,440 --> 00:14:32,680
once swollen up.

172
00:14:47,680 --> 00:14:48,480
Physician,

173
00:14:51,080 --> 00:14:54,000
check if this little wretch
is pretending.

174
00:14:54,360 --> 00:14:55,160
Yes.

175
00:15:03,240 --> 00:15:04,320
Your Majesty,

176
00:15:04,840 --> 00:15:05,600
she's...

177
00:15:06,200 --> 00:15:07,280
She's pregnant.

178
00:15:09,160 --> 00:15:09,960
What?

179
00:15:10,320 --> 00:15:13,800
She's been pregnant for over a month.

180
00:15:25,040 --> 00:15:25,840
Waiter.

181
00:15:26,200 --> 00:15:27,000
Coming.

182
00:15:28,480 --> 00:15:29,280
Sir.

183
00:15:30,680 --> 00:15:31,800
Prepare a carriage for me.

184
00:15:31,880 --> 00:15:32,880
I need to return to Andu.

185
00:15:33,800 --> 00:15:34,360
Sir,

186
00:15:35,720 --> 00:15:37,240
but you're injured

187
00:15:37,320 --> 00:15:38,720
and Andu is far away.

188
00:15:38,800 --> 00:15:40,440
Shouldn't you rest for a few days?

189
00:15:40,760 --> 00:15:42,680
A rushed journey could be
too much for you.

190
00:15:43,680 --> 00:15:45,360
My bride-to-be is waiting
for me in Andu.

191
00:15:45,880 --> 00:15:47,320
This time,

192
00:15:47,520 --> 00:15:48,680
I'm going back to marry her.

193
00:15:50,160 --> 00:15:51,560
Understood, I'll arrange it right away.

194
00:15:55,520 --> 00:15:58,680
Even if it's through fire and water,
I must go.

195
00:16:25,240 --> 00:16:27,430
♪The wind under the eaves♪

196
00:16:27,900 --> 00:16:30,540
♪Gently taps on the wooden door♪

197
00:16:32,290 --> 00:16:34,770
♪The candle flame flickers
as I sleep soundly♪

198
00:16:35,070 --> 00:16:37,450
♪The night is at its peak♪

199
00:16:39,310 --> 00:16:41,560
♪A thunderclap rolls♪

200
00:16:42,030 --> 00:16:44,490
♪Stirring up old dreams again♪

201
00:16:46,630 --> 00:16:48,990
♪Thoughts linger
on the warmth of the past♪

202
00:16:49,180 --> 00:16:52,420
♪The sincerity of the past♪

203
00:16:52,610 --> 00:16:55,770
♪Fireworks fall like rain♪

204
00:16:56,040 --> 00:16:59,040
♪But soon they cool♪

205
00:16:59,590 --> 00:17:03,280
♪I watch as you pass by♪

206
00:17:03,300 --> 00:17:06,390
♪Not daring to ask♪

207
00:17:06,920 --> 00:17:10,210
♪Like the moon, waxing and waning♪

208
00:17:10,210 --> 00:17:13,280
♪How could it ask more?♪

209
00:17:13,550 --> 00:17:18,470
♪You and I are like a small boat
on the river♪

210
00:17:18,730 --> 00:17:23,480
♪Rising and falling with the waves♪

211
00:17:46,390 --> 00:17:48,930
♪Speaking of love and hate♪

212
00:17:49,270 --> 00:17:51,760
♪How can I distinguish them?♪

213
00:17:53,660 --> 00:17:56,050
♪Longing for fate, praying sincerely♪

214
00:17:56,350 --> 00:17:59,400
♪Yet the world does not acknowledge it♪

215
00:18:00,460 --> 00:18:02,820
♪The night grows deep♪

216
00:18:03,230 --> 00:18:06,060
♪Old dreams are stirred again♪

217
00:18:07,830 --> 00:18:10,270
♪Yet the previous ones
are still within them♪

218
00:18:10,460 --> 00:18:13,530
♪Why do they remain silent?♪

219
00:18:13,850 --> 00:18:16,950
♪Fireworks fall like rain♪

220
00:18:17,330 --> 00:18:20,360
♪But soon they cool♪

221
00:18:20,830 --> 00:18:24,540
♪I look, adding a few more strokes
to the word "love"♪

222
00:18:24,710 --> 00:18:27,680
♪A new year's ring♪

223
00:18:28,000 --> 00:18:31,310
♪The cicada's cry is close,
autumn leaves are near♪

224
00:18:31,530 --> 00:18:34,480
♪Yet it's hard to recognize each other♪

225
00:18:35,100 --> 00:18:39,690
♪I sigh, why are you and I♪

226
00:18:40,260 --> 00:18:44,800
♪Rising and falling,
drifting in this way?♪
